race.comment: Plenty of win chances but sticking with SOMETHING FORJO (6). Last start winner here when got back but stormed home and has a good record course and distance. Aided by the claim and with plenty of pace looks tough to stop again. CHEERFUL CAT (7) doesn't win out of turn but very much overdue. Good in all three runs this time, the last two beaten in a photo. Just needs to run up to that again to feature. BURLEIGH MAGIC (2) is much better than last start. Not far away both starts prior and does have a very good record at the mile. Can improve sharply. GOING TO THE SUN (8) has been racing over further then dropped back to 1400m latest and ran on well. This suits better and will wind up late. RAMPANT LION (4) is suited by the trip as well and drawn for a good run off the low draw.
